title: #92Noon Nordo in for PA - Russo, Wobby, Leber, Bersich, PA, Cliff
description: Recap of the inspiring Army/Navy game over the weekend. Michael Russo weighs in on the the recent dysfunction of the Wild. NF-L'S of the week. The Vikings are in Seattle tonight to take on the Seahawks. Wobby, Leber, Bersich, PA and former Seahawk, Cliff Avril check in from Seattle, in that order. PA and Nordo reminisce with Cliff.
